# Inventory Service (Worker) T

The backend worker responsible for the heavy lifting (Orbital Mechanics & Resource Management).

## Key Features

* **Event Consumer:** Listens to `orbit-tasks-queue` for new jobs.
* **Idempotency Check:** Prevents duplicate processing of the same message using a unique ID check.
* **Business Logic:** Simulates orbit propagation and fuel checks.
* **Reactive Feedback:** Publishes the result (Success/Failure) back to the system to complete the Saga.

## Configuration
Runs on port **8081**. It is not directly exposed to the user (Worker pattern).